# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# FastAPI Repository Chat Agent — Environment Configuration
# Copy to .env and fill in secrets. NEVER commit .env to version control.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── REQUIRED: OpenAI API Key ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get your API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
OPENAI_MAX_TOKENS=4096
OPENAI_TEMPERATURE=0.1
OPENAI_TIMEOUT=60.0
OPENAI_MAX_RETRIES=3

# ── Neo4j Database ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Password must match NEO4J_AUTH in docker-compose.yml
NEO4J_URI=bolt://localhost:7687
NEO4J_USERNAME=neo4j
NEO4J_PASSWORD=securepassword123
NEO4J_DATABASE=neo4j
NEO4J_MAX_POOL_SIZE=50
NEO4J_CONN_TIMEOUT=30
NEO4J_MAX_TX_RETRY=3

# ── SHARED: Redis ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379/0
REDIS_MAX_CONNECTIONS=20
REDIS_SESSION_TTL=86400                       # 24 hours (sliding)
REDIS_CACHE_TTL=3600                          # 1 hour response cache
REDIS_MAX_MESSAGES_PER_SESSION=200
REDIS_SOCKET_TIMEOUT=5

# ── SHARED: Retry policy ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
RETRY_MAX_ATTEMPTS=3
RETRY_WAIT_MIN=1.0                            # seconds
RETRY_WAIT_MAX=10.0
RETRY_MULTIPLIER=1.5
RETRY_ON_TIMEOUT=true
RETRY_ON_SERVER_ERROR=true

# ── GATEWAY ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GATEWAY_HOST=0.0.0.0
GATEWAY_PORT=8000
GATEWAY_ENVIRONMENT=development              # development | testing | production
GATEWAY_LOG_LEVEL=INFO                       # DEBUG | INFO | WARNING | ERROR
GATEWAY_SECRET_KEY=change-me-in-production   # REQUIRED in production
GATEWAY_CORS_ORIGINS=["*"]                   # ["https://yourdomain.com"] in prod
GATEWAY_WS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=[]               # [] = allow all (dev only)
GATEWAY_RATE_LIMIT_PER_MINUTE=60
GATEWAY_AGENT_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=90.0
GATEWAY_STREAM_CHUNK_CHARS=40
GATEWAY_DEFAULT_REPO_URL=https://github.com/fastapi/fastapi.git

# Downstream agent URLs (use Docker service names in compose)
GATEWAY_ORCHESTRATOR_URL=http://orchestrator:8001
GATEWAY_INDEXER_URL=http://indexer:8002
GATEWAY_GRAPH_QUERY_URL=http://graph-query:8003
GATEWAY_CODE_ANALYST_URL=http://code-analyst:8004

# ── ORCHESTRATOR ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ORCHESTRATOR_HOST=0.0.0.0
ORCHESTRATOR_PORT=8001
ORCHESTRATOR_ENVIRONMENT=development
ORCHESTRATOR_LOG_LEVEL=INFO
ORCHESTRATOR_SYNTHESIS_MODEL=gpt-4o          # higher quality for final answer
ORCHESTRATOR_ANALYSIS_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini      # fast for intent classification
ORCHESTRATOR_OPENAI_MAX_TOKENS=4096
ORCHESTRATOR_MAX_PARALLEL_AGENTS=3
ORCHESTRATOR_AGENT_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=60.0
ORCHESTRATOR_INDEXER_URL=http://indexer:8002
ORCHESTRATOR_GRAPH_QUERY_URL=http://graph-query:8003
ORCHESTRATOR_CODE_ANALYST_URL=http://code-analyst:8004
ORCHESTRATOR_CONTEXT_WINDOW_MESSAGES=5
ORCHESTRATOR_MAX_ENTITY_CONTEXT=10

# ── INDEXER ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
INDEXER_HOST=0.0.0.0
INDEXER_PORT=8002
INDEXER_ENVIRONMENT=development
INDEXER_LOG_LEVEL=INFO
INDEXER_REPO_URL=https://github.com/fastapi/fastapi.git
INDEXER_REPO_LOCAL_PATH=/tmp/fastapi_repo
INDEXER_GIT_DEPTH=1
INDEXER_GIT_TIMEOUT=300
INDEXER_MAX_FILE_SIZE_KB=500
INDEXER_MAX_CONCURRENT_FILES=10
INDEXER_INCLUDE_TEST_FILES=false
INDEXER_INCLUDE_PATTERNS=["*.py"]
INDEXER_EXCLUDE_PATTERNS=["**/test_*.py","**/__pycache__/**","**/migrations/**"]
INDEXER_SOURCE_SNIPPET_MAX_KB=8

# ── GRAPH QUERY ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GRAPH_QUERY_HOST=0.0.0.0
GRAPH_QUERY_PORT=8003
GRAPH_QUERY_ENVIRONMENT=development
GRAPH_QUERY_LOG_LEVEL=INFO
GRAPH_QUERY_RESULT_LIMIT=50
GRAPH_QUERY_MAX_QUERY_DEPTH=5
GRAPH_QUERY_ALLOWED_QUERY_PREFIXES=["MATCH"]
GRAPH_QUERY_CACHE_QUERY_RESULTS=true
GRAPH_QUERY_CACHE_TTL_SECONDS=300
GRAPH_QUERY_QUERY_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=30.0

# ── CODE ANALYST ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CODE_ANALYST_HOST=0.0.0.0
CODE_ANALYST_PORT=8004
CODE_ANALYST_ENVIRONMENT=development
CODE_ANALYST_LOG_LEVEL=INFO
CODE_ANALYST_ANALYSIS_MODEL=gpt-4o
CODE_ANALYST_MAX_SOURCE_CHARS=3500
CODE_ANALYST_MAX_SNIPPET_LINES=150
CODE_ANALYST_SNIPPET_CONTEXT_LINES=10
CODE_ANALYST_ENABLE_CACHE=true
CODE_ANALYST_CACHE_TTL=1800